code: @Override protected NamedValueInfo createNamedValueInfo(MethodParameter parameter) {     Value ann = parameter.getParameterAnnotation(Value.class).     Assert.state(ann != null, "No Value annotation").     return new ExpressionValueNamedValueInfo(ann). }
@Override @Nullable protected Object resolveName(String name, MethodParameter parameter, NativeWebRequest webRequest) throws Exception {     // No name to resolve     return null. }

@Override protected void handleMissingValue(String name, MethodParameter parameter) throws ServletException {     throw new UnsupportedOperationException("@Value is never required: " + parameter.getMethod()). }
